data.description: Welcome to 9417 27th Bay St, located in Norfolk's idyllic East Beach community!  This corner townhome features 2 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms in 1687 sq ft of living space.  The first floor features a light-filled bedroom with attached bath, the laundry room, and garage access. The second floor contains the primary suite and an open-concept kitchen with stainless steel appliances as well as a spacious living area. The top level boasts two large storage areas (one finished, one unfinished) as well as a loft currently utilized as an office. This home is filled with upgraded fixtures and quality finishes.  East Beach amenities include beach access (2 blocks away!), pool, fitness center, playgrounds, and clubhouse.  Conveniently located in close proximity to Norfolk's Navy bases, East Beach's shopping and restaurants, and all that Norfolk and Virginia Beach have to offer.  *Assumable VA loan - see agent notes for details*
